# Sentinel environment configuration — copy to `.env` (git-ignored) and fill in.
# Only non-default / deployment-specific values need to be set; everything here
# has a working default in backend/config.py.
#
# Digital decode (the dsd-fme sidecar) needs NO configuration: the ingest secret
# is auto-generated by the backend and shared with the decoder via a Docker
# volume. To pin an explicit secret instead, uncomment and set this (compose
# passes it to both the backend and the decoder):
# SENTINEL_DECODER_SECRET=
